### Notes

- `title` (required) - The post title
- `date` (required) - Publication date in YYYY-MM-DD format
- `description` (required) - Used for SEO meta description and post previews
- `coverImage` (optional) - Path to cover image in /public/blog/
- `tags` (optional) - Array of tags for categorization

Images should be placed in `/public/blog/` and referenced with absolute paths.
